gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 130, Pelicans 102
gameRecap.excerpt: Stephen Curry led the Warriors with 42 points (7-13 3PT FG), five rebounds, and five assists as Chris Paul added 13 points, six rebounds, and five assists for the Warriors as they defeated the Pelicans, 130-102. CJ McCollum led the Pelicans with 19 points, six rebounds, and five assists while Zion Williamson totaled 19 points, five rebounds, and three assists. The Warriors improve to 3-1 as the Pelicans fall to 2-1.
